java, python, c and c++.As you know, I'm so greedy that nothing can 
be done.but,don't laugh at me , i am trying to keeping work hard.    

        I also want to have a cool life.    
i need to go out to find the beauty of the world. i will cultivate some hobbies,beacause 
i know i have miss many things. at last ,forgive for my pool english
